  "texts": [
    "The average ONR of DIRTY is 76.7% while the total ONR of DeGPT is 93.6%.",
    "Regarding MVR, the values of DIRTY are between 6.2% and 16.5%, with an average MVR is 11.1%, which is lower than DeGPT's 30.3%.",
    "The results show that DeGPT can allocate more meaningful names to more variables than DIRTY.",
    "Through in-depth analysis, we found two main reasons for the restricted efficacy of DIRTY.",
    "(i) Limited training dataset leads to its limited prediction capability."
